{
  "title": "audio",
  "audio": "sounds/audio.mp3",
  "duration": 121.12,
  "segments": [
    {
      "id": 0,
      "start": 0.1,
      "end": 2.24,
      "text": "今回はMAX初心者でも無料",
      "scene": "surprised",
      "character": 0,
      "emphasis": null,
      "sound": "sounds/se_intro.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": 1,
      "start": 2.82,
      "end": 6.46,
      "text": "でAI動画を作れる環境を実際にゼロから作っていきます。",
      "scene": "pointing",
      "character": 1,
      "emphasis": null,
      "sound": "sounds/se_achievement.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "start": 6.76,
      "end": 9.32,
      "text": "しかも今回言えるのはほぼコピペだけです。",
      "scene": "surprised",
      "character": 0,
      "emphasis": null,
      "sound": "sounds/se_impact.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "start": 9.71,
      "end": 12.43,
      "text": "まず概要欄のGitHubを\n開きます。",
      "scene": "surprised",
      "character": 0,
      "emphasis": null,
      "sound": "sounds/se_treasure.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "start": 12.8,
      "end": 14,
      "text": "するとこんな画面が出ます。",
      "scene": "surprised",
      "character": 0,
      "emphasis": null,
      "sound": null
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "start": 14.48,
      "end": 16.74,
      "text": "英語いっぱいでちょっと難しそうに見えますよね。",
      "scene": "surprised",
      "character": 0,
      "emphasis": null,
      "sound": "sounds/se_sigh.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": 6,
      "start": 17.18,
      "end": 18.2,
      "text": "でも安心してください。",
      "scene": "smile",
      "character": 3,
      "emphasis": null,
      "sound": null
    },
    {
      "id": 7,
      "start": 18.8,
      "end": 21.6,
      "text": "初心者の人が使うのはこの緑のボタンだけです。",
      "scene": "surprised",
      "character": 0,
      "emphasis": null,
      "sound": "sounds/se_impact.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": 8,
      "start": 22.14,
      "end": 23.68,
      "text": "このコードボタンを\n押します。",
      "scene": "surprised",
      "character": 0,
      "emphasis": null,
      "sound": "sounds/se_pikon.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": 9,
      "start": 23.88,
      "end": 27.36,
      "text": "するとダウンロード、ZIPが出るのでこれを\nクリック。",
      "scene": "pointing",
      "character": 1,
      "emphasis": null,
      "sound": "sounds/se_drum.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": 10,
      "start": 27.68,
      "end": 29.3,
      "text": "はい、これでダウンロードを\n開始です。",
      "scene": "pointing",
      "character": 1,
      "emphasis": null,
      "sound": "sounds/se_fanfare.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": 11,
      "start": 29.96,
      "end": 32.48,
      "text": "右上にZIPファイルが\n出ました。",
      "scene": "pointing",
      "character": 1,
      "emphasis": null,
      "sound": "sounds/se_pikon.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": 12,
      "start": 32.66,
      "end": 34.58,
      "text": "ここ初心者の方めちゃめちゃ大事です。",
      "scene": "pointing",
      "character": 1,
      "emphasis": null,
      "sound": "sounds/se_impact.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": 13,
      "start": 35.28,
      "end": 37.8,
      "text": "本当にダウンロードできた？って不安になるので、ちゃんと",
      "scene": "pointing",
      "character": 1,
      "emphasis": null,
      "sound": null
    },
    {
      "id": 14,
      "start": 38.48,
      "end": 39.78,
      "text": "ここで確認してください。",
      "scene": "smile",
      "character": 3,
      "emphasis": null,
      "sound": null
    },
    {
      "id": 15,
      "start": 39.92,
      "end": 42.68,
      "text": "次はこのZIPフォルダをダブルクリックします。",
      "scene": "pointing",
      "character": 1,
      "emphasis": null,
      "sound": null
    },
    {
      "id": 16,
      "start": 42.88,
      "end": 44.16,
      "text": "するとはい、フォルダが出ました。",
      "scene": "pointing",
      "character": 1,
      "emphasis": null,
      "sound": "sounds/se_fanfare.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": 17,
      "start": 44.46,
      "end": 45.4,
      "text": "これが本体です。",
      "scene": "pointing",
      "character": 1,
      "emphasis": null,
      "sound": null
    },
    {
      "id": 18,
      "start": 45.84,
      "end": 49.6,
      "text": "ここにAI動画を作るための全部のデータが入っています。",
      "scene": "surprised",
      "character": 0,
      "emphasis": null,
      "sound": null
    },
    {
      "id": 19,
      "start": 49.76,
      "end": 53.24,
      "text": "ここまできたら次はNode.jsを入れます。",
      "scene": "pointing",
      "character": 1,
      "emphasis": null,
      "sound": "sounds/se_notice.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": 20,
      "start": 53.57,
      "end": 58.62,
      "text": "これはこのツールを\n動かすためのエンジン\nみたいなものです。",
      "scene": "pointing",
      "character": 1,
      "emphasis": null,
      "sound": null
    },
    {
      "id": 21,
      "start": 58.86,
      "end": 60.7,
      "text": "難しく考えなくてもOKです。",
      "scene": "thinking",
      "character": 2,
      "emphasis": null,
      "sound": null
    },
    {
      "id": 22,
      "start": 61.6,
      "end": 62.4,
      "text": "GoogleでNode.jsと",
      "scene": "thinking",
      "character": 2,
      "emphasis": null,
      "sound": null
    },
    {
      "id": 23,
      "start": 63.1,
      "end": 64.44,
      "text": "検索してください。",
      "scene": "smile",
      "character": 3,
      "emphasis": null,
      "sound": null
    },
    {
      "id": 24,
      "start": 64.82,
      "end": 69,
      "text": "公式サイトを開いたらLTSと書いてある方を押します。",
      "scene": "thinking",
      "character": 2,
      "emphasis": null,
      "sound": "sounds/se_impact.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": 25,
      "start": 69.62,
      "end": 72.25,
      "text": "ダウンロードしたら普通のアプリみたいにインストールしてください。",
      "scene": "smile",
      "character": 3,
      "emphasis": null,
      "sound": null
    },
    {
      "id": 26,
      "start": 72.48,
      "end": 76.7,
      "text": "ここまできたらMac右上の\n虫眼鏡を押してターミナルと入力します。",
      "scene": "thinking",
      "character": 2,
      "emphasis": null,
      "sound": null
    },
    {
      "id": 27,
      "start": 77.04,
      "end": 79.1,
      "text": "するとこの黒い画面が出ます",
      "scene": "thinking",
      "character": 2,
      "emphasis": null,
      "sound": "sounds/se_drum.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": 28,
      "start": 79.4,
      "end": 81.04,
      "text": "ここみんな最初ビビります。",
      "scene": "thinking",
      "character": 2,
      "emphasis": null,
      "sound": null
    },
    {
      "id": 29,
      "start": 81.9,
      "end": 84.44,
      "text": "でも今日はコピペしかやらないので安心してください。",
      "scene": "smile",
      "character": 3,
      "emphasis": null,
      "sound": null
    },
    {
      "id": 30,
      "start": 84.6,
      "end": 87.18,
      "text": "次にさっき解凍したフォルダに移動します。",
      "scene": "thinking",
      "character": 2,
      "emphasis": null,
      "sound": null
    },
    {
      "id": 31,
      "start": 87.94,
      "end": 89.3,
      "text": "もしエラーが出ても\n大丈夫です。",
      "scene": "smile",
      "character": 3,
      "emphasis": null,
      "sound": null
    },
    {
      "id": 32,
      "start": 89.9,
      "end": 90.92,
      "text": "初心者みんな出ます。",
      "scene": "thinking",
      "character": 2,
      "emphasis": null,
      "sound": null
    },
    {
      "id": 33,
      "start": 91.36,
      "end": 96.24,
      "text": "エラーが出たら必要な部品を追加してるだけなので落ち着いて進めるのが大丈夫です。",
      "scene": "smile",
      "character": 3,
      "emphasis": null,
      "sound": null
    },
    {
      "id": 34,
      "start": 97.22,
      "end": 102.68,
      "text": "そして最後にNPM run DEVを実行します。",
      "scene": "smile",
      "character": 3,
      "emphasis": null,
      "sound": null
    },
    {
      "id": 35,
      "start": 103.04,
      "end": 104.06,
      "text": "すると「おー」出ました。",
      "scene": "smile",
      "character": 3,
      "emphasis": null,
      "sound": "sounds/se_sugoi.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": 36,
      "start": 104.4,
      "end": 104.54,
      "text": "これです。",
      "scene": "smile",
      "character": 3,
      "emphasis": null,
      "sound": null
    },
    {
      "id": 37,
      "start": 105.14,
      "end": 107.78,
      "text": "これがAI動画を作る\n画面です。",
      "scene": "pointing",
      "character": 1,
      "emphasis": null,
      "sound": null
    },
    {
      "id": 38,
      "start": 107.9,
      "end": 108.94,
      "text": "ここまできたら成功です。",
      "scene": "pointing",
      "character": 1,
      "emphasis": null,
      "sound": "sounds/se_achievement.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": 39,
      "start": 109.2,
      "end": 110.1,
      "text": "しかもこれ無料です。",
      "scene": "smile",
      "character": 3,
      "emphasis": null,
      "sound": "sounds/se_treasure.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": 40,
      "start": 110.66,
      "end": 113.7,
      "text": "右下を見るとレンダーボタンがあります。",
      "scene": "smile",
      "character": 3,
      "emphasis": null,
      "sound": null
    },
    {
      "id": 41,
      "start": 114.38,
      "end": 116.96,
      "text": "つまりここから実際にショート動画を書き出せます。",
      "scene": "pointing",
      "character": 1,
      "emphasis": null,
      "sound": null
    },
    {
      "id": 42,
      "start": 117.6,
      "end": 121.12,
      "text": "次回はCSVを読み込んで\n実際にショート動画を作っていきます。",
      "scene": "pointing",
      "character": 1,
      "emphasis": null,
      "sound": "sounds/se_fanfare.mp3"
    }
  ],
